# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:20
translate korean e04s08_42cc5e2a:

    # mc "It is a pleasure to see you."
    mc "정말 잘 오셨습니다."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:22
translate korean e04s08_bb47e4fc:

    # jdg "I bet. I take it your first prisoner is doing well?"
    jdg "이렇게 나오는 걸 보면, 첫 번째 죄수가 잘 하고 있나 봐?"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:24
translate korean e04s08_0bce0934:

    # mc "Indeed. If she were up for parole I'm sure any board would release her."
    mc "그럼요. 어떤 가석방 위원회라도 석방해 줄 정도죠."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:28
translate korean e04s08_6ab7cea7:

    # jdg "I wonder if that is what she wants."
    jdg "걔가 그걸 원하는진 모르겠네."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:30
translate korean e04s08_2753cbc6:

    # mc "If I have done my job properly-"
    mc "제대로 일을 했으니-"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:31
translate korean e04s08_a18481e4:

    # jdg "Have you given any thought to where your prisoners will go next?"
    jdg "네 죄수들이 어디로 이제 어디로 가게 될지 생각해 본 적은 있니?"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:34
translate korean e04s08_5c30c0d3:

    # mc "I'm sure you'll provide something appropriate."
    mc "그거야 판사님께서 적절한 장소를 마련해 주시겠죠."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:36
translate korean e04s08_575630df:

    # jdg "You're not worried about losing your favorite toy?"
    jdg "네가 가장 좋아하는 장난감을 잃을 걱정되는 하는 건 아니지?"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:38
translate korean e04s08_1b0b79f1:

    # mc "She is my favorite toy. I doubt she'll go far."
    mc "제가 좋아하는 덴 이유가 있죠. 멀리 가지는 않을 겁니다."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:41
translate korean e04s08_44b9009c:

    # jdg "Well, you don't have to worry about that."
    jdg "뭐, 네가 걱정할 일은 없어."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:42
translate korean e04s08_2492d132:

    # jdg "Part of her conviction turned this property over to the Court."
    jdg "일부 유죄 판결에 따라 이 부동산은 법원에 귀속되었거든."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:44
translate korean e04s08_adf0061b:

    # mc "So I can keep using it as a prison?"
    mc "그 말씀은 이곳을 계속 감옥으로 써도 된다는 말씀이죠?"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:47
translate korean e04s08_0e91b756:

    # jdg "Indeed. I wouldn't have given you so many female prisoners otherwise."
    jdg "맞아. 감옥이니까, 이렇게 많은 여성 죄수들을 너한테 준 거 아니겠니."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:49
translate korean e04s08_f77e85f8:

    # mc "Excellent. How long will this last?"
    mc "멋지네요. 기한은 어떻게 되나요?"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:50
translate korean e04s08_aa54ff21:

    # jdg "As long as you continue to impress me."
    jdg "네가 나한테 좋은 인상을 남기는 한 계속."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:53
translate korean e04s08_ba65fe55:

    # mc "Excellent."
    mc "훌륭하네요."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:61
translate korean e04s08_26824b28:

    # sy "It's almost a shame she's getting released today."
    sy "그년이 오늘 풀려난다는 게 아쉬울 정도인걸."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:62
translate korean e04s08_dfab14a8:

    # sy "Almost nothing is quite as enjoyable as torturing her."
    sy "걔 고문하는 것만큼 즐거운 일도 거의 없는데 말이야."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:65
translate korean e04s08_1090ee2a:

    # arj "Isn't there anything we can do? Can't she stay here as a willing prisoner like I am?"
    arj "우리가 어떻게 할 수는 없을까? 나처럼 자발적으로 죄수가 될 수도 있잖아?"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:67
translate korean e04s08_b0b27436:

    # sy "I don't know. Above my pay grade."
    sy "그건 잘 모르겠네. 내 짬에 신경 쓸 일도 아니고."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:70
translate korean e04s08_5dfa74a6:

    # arj "That's a shame. I'm going to miss her."
    arj "정말 아쉽다. 리디아가 그리울 거야."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:72
translate korean e04s08_b15419ad:

    # sy "It's between the warden and the judge, I guess. Maybe she has a say in that too."
    sy "소장님과 판사님께서 알아서 하시겠지. 리디아의 의향도 중요하겠지만."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:76
translate korean e04s08_b6ac9444:

    # sy "Alright, let's get you out of there."
    sy "좋아, 이제 나가자구."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:77
translate korean e04s08_6fe00a6b:

    # sy "Prisoner 001! The Judge is here. You're getting released."
    sy "죄수 번호 001! 판사님이 도착하셨다. 넌 석방된다."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:79
translate korean e04s08_16cf56e7:

    # lc "Huh?"
    lc "어?"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:83
translate korean e04s08_4a0a0920:

    # sy "You've served out your sentence. You're going to be a free woman."
    sy "넌 형기를 다 채웠다. 이제 자유의 몸될 거라고."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:85
translate korean e04s08_8515f081:

    # lc "Oh."
    lc "아."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:87
translate korean e04s08_2b03f0d4:

    # sy "Well, once we get you to the Warden."
    sy "흠, 일단 소장님께 데려다 주지."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:91
translate korean e04s08_31883444:

    # lc "[alt_mcname]? Of course! Right away!"
    lc "[alt_mcname]? 물론이죠! 바로 가요!"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:93
translate korean e04s08_7d64e5cc:

    # sy "Good girl. Let's go."
    sy "착하네. 이제 가자."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:96
translate korean e04s08_66d71020:

    # sy "I brought you the prisoner scheduled for release."
    sy "석방 예정인 죄수를 데리고 왔습니다."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:98
translate korean e04s08_3dbc6344:

    # mc "Well done."
    mc "잘 했어."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:100
translate korean e04s08_1c1abd34:

    # jdg "Why is the other one here?"
    jdg "다른 것들은 왜 여기에 있는 거니?"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:103
translate korean e04s08_90743772:

    # sy "Prisoner 002? She follows me around wherever I go, like a faithful puppy."
    sy "죄수 번호 002 말씀이세요? 제가 어디를 가든 항상 따라다니거든요, 충성심 강한 강아지 같죠."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:105
translate korean e04s08_566eae01:

    # jdg "I see."
    jdg "그렇군."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:107
translate korean e04s08_0acac678:

    # mc "She's one of the willing prisoners. There's no risk involved."
    mc "자발적으로 죄수가 된 사람 중 한 명입니다. 위험 요소는 전혀 없습니다."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:110
translate korean e04s08_5b40fcb8:

    # jdg "Very well. Let's get this started."
    jdg "그럼 좋아. 이제 시작해 볼까."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:112
translate korean e04s08_1a66c9d9:

    # mc "Prisoner 001 - Stand and face the Judge."
    mc "죄수 번호 001 - 일어서서 판사님을 향해라."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:115
translate korean e04s08_8f19cc5b:

    # jdg "Very good. Lydia Cox, you have served out the term of your sentence."
    jdg "아주 좋습니다. 리디아 칵스, 귀하는 형기를 모두 마쳤습니다."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:116
translate korean e04s08_73e3a881:

    # jdg "I have signed your release papers and you are free to leave."
    jdg "본 판사는 석방 서류에 서명했으며, 귀하는 이제 자유롭게 떠날 수 있습니다."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:119
translate korean e04s08_bab9f5c4:

    # lc "[alt_mcname]? I don't understand. What's happening?"
    lc "[alt_mcname]? 저 이게 무슨 일인지 모르겠어요. 무슨 일이죠?"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:121
translate korean e04s08_745a7c78:

    # mc "You are getting your freedom. You are no longer a prisoner here."
    mc "이제 자유를 얻었다 소리야. 이제 더 이상 이곳의 죄수가 아니라는 거지."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:124
translate korean e04s08_f1135052:

    # jdg "Now, there can be some difficulties re-entering society, but having reviewed your finances I am confident that you have the necessary means."
    jdg "물론 사회에 복귀하는 데 어려움이 있을 수 있겠습니다만, 귀하의 재정 상태를 검토한 바, 사회 복귀에 필요한 수단은 모두 갖추었으리라 봅니다."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:125
translate korean e04s08_45bc88a2:

    # jdg "You're a rather wealthy woman, Miss Cox."
    jdg "칵스 씨 당신은 상당히 부유한 여성입니다."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:128
translate korean e04s08_2ac94a06:

    # jdg "I know an excellent lawyer who is also involved in real estate."
    jdg "본 판사는 부동산에도 전문성을 갖춘 훌륭한 변호사를 알고 있습니다."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:129
translate korean e04s08_c38f7882:

    # jdg "I'll convince her to help you reacclimate to normal life."
    jdg "해당 변호사에게 권유하여 정상적인 삶에 다시 적응할 수 있도록 돕게 하겠습니다."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:134
translate korean e04s08_f8f47060:

    # jdg "Oh, there she is now."
    jdg "아, 저기에 있네요."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:135
translate korean e04s08_a1498851:

    # jdg "Hmm. Looks like she is occupied at the moment."
    jdg "흐으음. 당장은 바쁜 모양이군요."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:138
translate korean e04s08_ae498221:

    # jdg "She will call you tomorrow."
    jdg "해당 변호사가 내일 당신에게 연락할 것입니다."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:140
translate korean e04s08_ebfdf8a5:

    # mc "Is that everything?"
    mc "Is that everything?"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:141
translate korean e04s08_152a5e71:

    # jdg "I just need to return her personal effects and make sure she is properly dressed."
    jdg "출소자의 개인 소지품을 돌려주고 적절한 옷차림을 갖추게 하시오."
    
# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:142
translate korean e04s08_706e0030:

    # mc "Alright. After that we can walk her out."
    mc "알겠습니다. 그다음에 출소시키겠습니다."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:145
translate korean e04s08_a33ec19f:

    # jdg "Would you mind doing that? I would like to spend some time inspecting the prisoners."
    jdg "그 일은 네가 맡아 주겠니? 나는 죄수들을 점검하고 싶은데."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:147
translate korean e04s08_ef0c382f:

    # mc "Certainly. Enjoy yourself."
    mc "물론이죠. 즐거운 시간 보내세요."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:148
translate korean e04s08_6484d7c2:

    # jdg "Thank you. I certainly will."
    jdg "고마워. 그렇게 할게."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:158
translate korean e04s08_outside_30f8fcce:

    # mc "Give yourself a minute to get used to the sunlight."
    mc "햇볕에 적응하는 데 시간이 좀 걸릴 거야."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:159
translate korean e04s08_outside_1e857959:

    # mc "You haven't seen it in a while, have you?"
    mc "정말 오랜만에 보는 거잖아?"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:162
translate korean e04s08_outside_3a5f729b:

    # lc "It has been a while, [alt_mcname]."
    lc "정말 오랜만이네요, [alt_mcname]."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:163
translate korean e04s08_outside_48e4bb2b:

    # lc "I believe my eyes have adjusted."
    lc "이제 눈이 적응된 거 같아요."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:166
translate korean e04s08_outside_adffa7f0:

    # mc "I believe you remember the way from here."
    mc "여기서 나가는 길은 기억하고 있겠지."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:167
translate korean e04s08_outside_77e30104:

    # mc "There will be a taxi just outside the gate. It will take you anywhere you want."
    mc "대문 바로 밖에 택시가 있을 거야. 말만 하면 어디든지 데려다 줄 거고."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:168
translate korean e04s08_outside_cc6496f8:

    # mc "At this hour, I recommend getting a hotel."
    mc "이 시간대면, 호텔에 묵는 게 좋겠네."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:171
translate korean e04s08_outside_7c572e9d:

    # lc "Oh, um, okay."
    lc "아, 음, 알겠습니다."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:172
translate korean e04s08_outside_052c0e2f:

    # lc "Thank you, [alt_mcname]."
    lc "감사합니다, [alt_mcname]."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:176
translate korean e04s08_outside_dcb5b94d:

    # lc "I'll just be going then."
    lc "그럼 이만 가 볼게요."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:178
translate korean e04s08_outside_3177a2f8:

    # lc "I'll just be going..."
    lc "이만 가 볼게요..."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:180
translate korean e04s08_outside_07dbf68b:

    # lc "Heh. [alt_mcname] tried to drown me there when I first got here."
    lc "히. [alt_mcname], 그때가 생각나네요. 제가 여기에 처음 왔을 때 저를 익사시키려고 했잖아요."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:182
translate korean e04s08_outside_afa79b8c:

    # lc "When I first got here."
    lc "처음에 여기에 왔을 때라."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:184
translate korean e04s08_outside_6c3861a3:

    # lc "I almost forgot that I used to live here before it was a prison."
    lc "여기가 감옥이 되기 전에 나 여기에 살았었는데..."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:186
translate korean e04s08_outside_110b988e:

    # lc "Before it was his prison."
    lc "이 사람의 감옥이 되기 전에."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:187
translate korean e04s08_outside_bc8bf655:

    # lc "Before I was his."
    lc "내가 이 사람 것이 되기 전에."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:191
translate korean e04s08_outside_675153b2:

    # lc "This isn't right."
    lc "이러면 안 돼."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:192
translate korean e04s08_outside_40a3431a:

    # lc "I can't do this."
    lc "난 할 수 없어."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:195
translate korean e04s08_outside_d1f634bd:

    # mct "What is this?"
    mct "왜 저러지?"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:197
translate korean e04s08_outside_3d53b23a:

    # mc "Did you forget something?"
    mc "뭐 잊은 거라도 있어?"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:201
translate korean e04s08_outside_698fb84b:

    # lc "Don't make me go. Please don't make me go."
    lc "날 보내지 마. 제발 보내지 말아 줘."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:202
translate korean e04s08_outside_e64dbd20:

    # lc "I can't imagine life without you."
    lc "네가 없는 삶은 상상도 못하겠어."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:205
translate korean e04s08_outside_dd6f9968:

    # lc "I don't want to live without you."
    lc "너 없이 살고 싶지 않아."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:206
translate korean e04s08_outside_cb3d443a:

    # lc "Please let me stay."
    lc "제발 머물게 해 줘."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:208
translate korean e04s08_outside_a8722cbc:

    # mc "Lydia Cox - Get Up Now!"
    mc "리디아 칵스 - 당장 일어나!"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:212
translate korean e04s08_outside_be86ff27:

    # mc "Look At Me!"
    mc "날 봐!"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:215
translate korean e04s08_outside_2d726034:

    # mc "What am I going to do with you?"
    mc "내가 널 어떻게 해야 할까?"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:232
translate korean e04s08_upstairs_84387a45:

    # mct "That's my girl."
    mct "리디아는 내 여자야."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:233
translate korean e04s08_upstairs_d22ea6b7:

    # mct "She is finally completely mine."
    mct "그디어 완전히 내 것이 된 거야."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:241
translate korean e04s08_upstairs_6c13e6fb:

    # mc "C'mon, Lydia. Let's go inside."
    mc "자, 리디아. 안으로 들어가자."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:242
translate korean e04s08_upstairs_5f1d60a0:

    # mc "I've kept your bedroom just the way you left it."
    mc "네 방을 그대로 남겨 두었어."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:256
translate korean e04s08_downstairs_f992257c:

    # mc "Kiss my foot prisonar 001"
    mc "내 발에 입을 맞춰라, 죄수 번호 001"

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:262
translate korean e04s08_downstairs_b3abb371:

    # mc "Allright, prisoner. Let's go inside."
    mc "아주 좋아, 죄수. 안으로 들어가자."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:263
translate korean e04s08_downstairs_acd87584:

    # mc "We'll get you out of those clothes and back in your cage."
    mc "그 옷을 벗기고 다시 철창에 가두어 두지."

# game/code/e04/e04s08.rpy:277
